  lines:
  - speakerName: Silly
    englishSpeakerName: Silly
    text: "Con m\u00E8o b\u00EAn tr\u00E1i c\u00F3 v\u1EBB \u0111ang \u0111\u1EE3i c\u00E1. M\u00ECnh c\u1EA7n t\u00ECm c\u00E1 \u0111\u01B0a cho n\u00F3."
    englishText: The cat on the left looks like it wants fish. I should find a fish for it.
